Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Drozer console won't connect

Solution: Verify port forwarding with adb forward --list, restart Drozer agent on device, ensure emulator is fully booted
Issue: Commands timeout or hang

Solution: Increase timeout values in scripts, check device responsiveness with adb shell, restart ADB server with adb kill-server && adb start-server
Issue: No exposed components found

Solution: Verify target package is installed with adb shell pm list packages, ensure you're scanning the correct package name, try scanning all packages without -a flag
Issue: Python scripts fail to execute Drozer commands

Solution: Check Drozer is in PATH with which drozer, verify subprocess command syntax, test commands manually in Drozer console first
